=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afc48a94287d6a0aa9c517b6de7fdeaaf631d4e","tid":1396206,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"上個post 睇到巴打話坐緊監嘅人會互相分享經驗點俾人拉，<br />\n有冇貼士提醒下發夢嘅人點樣可以全身而退，<br />\n或者有冇啲好緊要嘅嘢發夢人士可能忽略咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bf7d5c5b17e71a9dc1184c47561175cbe636c0","tid":1396206,"uid":263395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e805e2706ffe93d3a8e7783ff350ca579bc64eb4","tid":1396206,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d1c2f619bf27ff2cac3c7c56ad9e48ec62efd04","tid":1396206,"uid":231413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b7188b13b09fe5b96f4aba630ab70907e771e53d","tid":1396206,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"901027692ed55dd525aed532d2bcaa0d2f19f528","tid":1396206,"uid":231413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"Wealtd 威富香煙<br />\n聽過未，淨係得荔枝角收押所附近士多先有得賣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"未 真係未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剩得呢隻牌子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵日買包試下監倉嘅味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"其實佢係專登要搵呢啲咁僻既牌子既，<br />\n原因係，如果入面俾食萬寶路，<br />\n咁柳記就會好容易而且低成本咁買煙入去俾犯，<br />\n因為管理古惑仔最容易既方法就係俾著數，<br />\n懲教署同警犬高層其實一直都知呢樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而依家食啲咁牌子，如果喺犯身上搵到萬寶路，<br />\n就一定懲教職員俾，無其他可能了。<br />\n<br />\n變左咁，懲教處前線管理期數既職員，<br />\n就算俾煙啲囚犯，都唔會俾咁大量，咁猖狂<br />\n懲教處紀律其實一直都十分差，<br />\n著名大哥肥波就試過踢竇踢到佢有電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/he